    <!-- Dialog instructions -->
    <string name="help_dialog_instructions">
        • Scan Receipt: capture a photo of a bill.\n
        • Extract Text: run OCR on the captured image.\n
        • Auto-Categorization: suggests a category; tap Save to store.\n
        • History: long-press an entry to delete; overflow → Export PDF.\n
        • Dashboard: visualize spending trends.\n
        • Use the “+” FAB to add a receipt manually.\n
        • Spending Alerts: set a spending-limit threshold; you’ll get a notification when you exceed it.\n
        • Calendar Entries: automatically add return or due-date events to your device calendar.
    </string>



